This paper discusses the field of data-to-text generation, which involves natural language generation from structured data. This topic falls under the category of natural language processing (NLP), which is covered by cs.CL (Computation and Language) in arXiv. The paper also discusses content selection methods, which involve machine learning and information retrieval techniques, falling under the categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing).
